des:
Cosas Inteligentes products help you control home appliance.You can simply ask Alexa to turn on or turn off your light.
There’s no need to go to the switch to adjust your light - just talk to Alexa on your Amazon Echo.
After connecting Alexa to your light products in a few simple steps:
(1). Download our "Cosas Inteligentes" app in android or ios app market;
(2). Register an account in our "Cosas Inteligentes" app;
(3). You need to have some Cosas Inteligentes devices in hand;
(4). Configure these devices in our "Cosas Inteligentes" app and change appropriate name for your devices which will be used in "Cosas Inteligentes iThings" skills;
(5). Download Amazon "Alexa" app from android,ios or Amazon app market;
(6). Configure Echo with "Alexa" app;
(7). Search "Cosas Inteligentes iThings" skill from the "Alexa" app skills category;
(8). Click Enable skill of "Cosas Inteligentes iThings", and you'll be navigated to "Cosas Inteligentes iThings" login page;
(9). Input your Cosas Inteligentes account username and password, you'll be redirect to the success page;
(10). Now all setup is finished.
You can enjoy the voice control on your home devices like these:
“Alexa, turn on the bedroom light.”
“Alexa, turn off the bedroom light.”
“Alexa, set the bedroom light to 50%.”
“Alexa, brighten the bedroom light to 50%.”
“Alexa, dim the bedroom light to 50%.”
"Alexa, set bedroom light to green."
"Alexa, set bedroom light to cool white."
